snippet.title: GoB 2020 (Official Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
(Game download links below!)
Interdimensional battles, alliances and enemies, titans and... Geese?

GoB is a character/class-based first/third-person shooter with over 25 playable characters and maps, along with over a hundred weapons.

This is a game that has been 4 years in the making. Experience GoB for yourself this September 17, 2020...

The trailer was made as a homage to the 4 years of development, showcasing every main map in the game in order of their appearance. (Aswell as areas from the campaign mode!) Only a handful of the 25+ characters have been featured in the trailer. 

The songs used during the montage of maps, and in the end credit section are both original songs featured on the game's soundtrack now available on Itunes, Spotify, Apple Music, and all major streaming services!

(Expect a music video, along with more GoB content soon)

Subscribe, like, and follow me on other social media for more updates on GoB, and future games from Sayincraft Studios!

GoB Official Discord: https://discord.gg/S3St6SF

GoB 2020 Soundtrack:
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/4hSxVECzYUKxg4n9to0ksi?si=UcVKJVjZS9mUATEutCgEFw
Itunes/Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/gob-2020-original-game-soundtrack-single/1531498491

***

GAME DOWNLOADS:
